overview: BarreAmped Boot Camp has helped hundreds of clients worldwide burn fat and lean out with classic barre combined with low impact, non-punishing cardio intervals. Suzanne Bowen, creator of BarreAmped, leads you through challenging but doable workout segments that can be done by themselves, mixed and matched, or all together for one incredible BarreAmped Boot Camp Fat Blast!
title: BarreAmped Boot Camp
